question: 입원 유형(응급/예약/긴급 등)별로 병원 사망률이 어떻게 다른지 알려줘.
expected_sql: SELECT a.admission_type, COUNT(*) AS hadm_cnt, AVG(a.hospital_expire_flag) AS hosp_mortality_rate FROM ADMISSIONS a JOIN PATIENTS p ON p.subject_id = a.subject_id GROUP BY a.admission_type ORDER BY hosp_mortality_rate DESC FETCH FIRST 20 ROWS ONLY

question: 중환자실 입원 기간동안 norepinephrine이 언제부터 언제까지 어떤 속도로 들어갔는지(시작/종료/속도) 타임라인 형태로 보여줘.
expected_sql: WITH norepi_item AS ( SELECT itemid FROM D_ITEMS WHERE LOWER(label) LIKE '%norepinephrine%' ) SELECT ie.stay_id, ie.starttime, ie.endtime, ie.rate, ie.rateuom FROM INPUTEVENTS ie JOIN norepi_item ni ON ni.itemid = ie.itemid WHERE ie.rate IS NOT NULL ORDER BY ie.stay_id, ie.starttime
